{"type": "article", "id": 20503, "title": "立方体墙饰", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-11T07:24:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122325K3UtZBz7paG24wQe.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是荷兰的设计事务所 STILES 推出的墙饰，将白桦木进行激光切割制作而成。每一小块是 6 边形，由 3 个菱形组合而成，而每一块菱形图案都有不同的纹路和深浅，贴在墙面上像是一个一个小的立方体，有很强的层次感，可以让墙面显得生动。每一套有 15 片，售价 32.58 美元，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/stiles-wall-decoration-set-of-15-tiles/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122324EvMpsWujziT0DwOn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122324U2yEYcXLRnrx0Cak.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}